    <h2 class="sect-title">About Country Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Developed in 1990, Country Hills is bound by the Harvest Hills Boulevard in the east, the Beddington trail in the south and the Country Hills Boulevard on the north.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">From single-family detached homes and townhomes to low rise apartments and condos, <span class="par-xl">the Country Hills homes for sale include a myriad of affordable options of residential units</span>. </p>
